    "description": "Are you a skilled Frontend Developer looking for your next big career move? BSNL Advisory Limited in Meerut offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout BSNL Advisory Limited:\nBSNL Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BSNL Advisory Limited!",
